Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.20,0:00:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明！暗號！陷阱！交易！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣組織超神秘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天步美面臨絕境！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.80,0:00:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論行動或推理 都是分秒必爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.40,0:00:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 卻擁有過人智慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SOS！來自步美的訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.10,0:01:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 抽中了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 我就抽這張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.60,0:01:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 又贏了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.00,0:01:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又是我和光彥兩個殿後啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.70,0:01:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下來要幹掉你了 光彥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕沒那麼容易喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.50,0:02:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.10,0:02:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 我～贏～了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 怎麼每次都是我輸啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光看你的表情 就連幼稚園的孩子都贏得過你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.50,0:02:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看小丑牌的時候和看其他牌的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.10,0:02:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直判若兩人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 柯南你真是的 怎麼可以說出來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們再玩一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次我從頭到尾都用這個表情來玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰原 你要不要一起玩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比較想看書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣人緣會變差喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還是這麼冷淡耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.90,0:03:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上在杯戶町發生了強盜殺人案耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說一家叫 “盧．愛司卡路”的法國餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女老闆被殺的案子吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.90,0:03:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼名字啊？還真怪耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.80,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“愛司卡路”在法文裡是指法國料理用的食用蝸牛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？蝸牛也可以吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非有蝸牛飯之類的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噁心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？你還知道什麼詳細情形嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.00,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 昨晚我聽到毛利叔叔和目暮警官關於這個案子的談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說被害人在接近中午的時候還在睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時強盜是撬開了鎖闖進去後 才發現被害人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 強盜當時是以為裡面沒人才進去的囉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.60,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者是在手腳被綁的情況下被刀刺殺身亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是兇手把她綁起來審問放錢的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.00,0:04:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢搶到手後 在離開前才殺死被害者的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.00,0:04:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為被害者看到他的臉 所以才起殺機嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人背脊發涼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.20,0:04:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手這麼殘暴 我看我們少年偵探團是派不上用場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.60,0:04:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.40,0:04:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來小孩子就不該在那裡高談闊論什麼殺人案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該多講點像夢想之類的小朋友的話題才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.70,0:04:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 你有沒有喉糖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你喉嚨痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.00,0:04:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 步美 你的聲音也有點怪怪的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 嘴巴張開 我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扁桃腺有點腫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有點發燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不是感冒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.00,0:04:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的話 吃點鰻魚飯很快就好了喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美又不是你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.50,0:05:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美 我看你還是先回家休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 回家好好休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.80,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.20,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也好 那我先去開車 你先在這裡等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在點名之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉田步美的媽媽剛才打過電話來替她請假 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美因為感冒所以要在家休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果真感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美她沒吃鰻魚飯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她昨天看起來臉色就很不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 你擔心她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦～真是溫柔體貼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.70,0:05:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 步美 媽媽有事要先出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會快點把事情辦好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中午之前就會回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要乖乖睡覺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 路上小…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.40,0:06:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 喉嚨消腫之後就可以說話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這邊是吉田家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在外出不便接電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請在“嗶”的一聲後留下姓名以及聯絡事項 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.20,0:07:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪位？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山本太太嗎？有您的包裹喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 媽媽回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對…不是媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她不會按門鈴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是強盜？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.80,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要報警…快打110…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切～原來是小孩子的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.90,0:09:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子 別躲了 出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會對你怎麼樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是柯南他們說的那個強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被他找到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就會跟“盧．愛司卡路”的老闆娘一樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.50,0:10:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學後 我們一起去探望步美吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我贊成！她一定會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很難說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.00,0:10:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女生最不希望自己情況很糟的時候被人看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是被自己喜歡的男生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.40,0:10:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.00,0:10:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我想小學生應該不在意這些吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她自己還不是小學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她大概在吹合唱要唱的曲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美 是你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是五號 早上十點三十分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是五號 早上十點三十分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是假面超人鬧鐘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是假面超人鬧鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前阿笠博士買給大家的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要按下超人頭上的按鈕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會自動報時、報日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.50,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼步美她自己不說話呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.00,0:11:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她該不會是沒聲音 無法說話了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？喂？步美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美 你現在不能說話了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.20,0:11:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是YES 就敲一下臂章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.60,0:11:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO的話就敲臂章兩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是YES
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的沒聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是覺得無聊 想聽聽我們的聲音吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們好好給她鼓勵一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她沒辦法說話 所以利用時鐘來出聲 這點我可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 剛才時鐘報時卻晚了五分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天也不是五號啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.90,0:12:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是步美有什麼事情想告訴我們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美 你那邊是不是遇到什麼麻煩事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美 如果是 YES 就敲一下臂章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.70,0:12:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO的話 就敲兩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是NO耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.30,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只太無聊 所以跟我們聯絡一下而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一節下課的時候 我們再跟你聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 下一節要去音樂教室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快點了 要是小林老師生氣起來 那可就不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到一個小孩子 居然有這麼先進的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 我想大家都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.10,0:13:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校下個月要舉辦校內音樂會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.00,0:13:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們B班是現場合唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.40,0:13:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們就先決定要唱什麼曲子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家有沒有什麼好建議呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有 我有 我有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心步美嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.10,0:13:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.20,0:13:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始那首曲子好像在哪裡聽過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有什麼印象？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我音樂還蠻爛的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個旋律是Mi Mi Re Do Re…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個先暫且擱下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼鬧鐘的日期和時間都不對呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是五日 早上十點三十分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五日…十點半…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.80,0:13:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 現在曲子也決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就先來唱一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點 點 小蟲 小蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小蝸牛蟲～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.50,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,(Mi Mi Re Do Re…)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是蝸牛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美她想告訴我們的是蝸牛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師 請你快報警！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美的生命有危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 江戶川同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.00,0:14:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！要是早點發現就好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個旋律指的就是蝸牛曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就暗示著“盧．愛司卡路”餐廳啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從日期和時間來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是想說強盜犯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.80,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,(五、十、三十的諧音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候步美一定是被強盜給抓住了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美 你那邊是不是遇到什麼麻煩事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美 如果是 YES 就敲一下臂章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO的話 就敲兩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你千萬要平安無事啊！步美！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 大致情形我都瞭解了 灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.70,0:15:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學 老師現在要去打電話報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家先在這邊安靜自習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元太！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走吧 光彥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.50,0:15:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！快沒時間了還給我紅燈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.00,0:15:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個強盜殺死老闆娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.30,0:15:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是把所有錢拿光 臨走前才下手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切～全部才七萬五千元啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.00,0:15:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你們住那麼大的公寓 居然只是金玉其外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了　
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也該善後、走人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這邊是吉田家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在外出不便接電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.30,0:16:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請在“嗶”聲後留下姓名以及聯絡事項 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在你家附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.00,0:16:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次我不是跟你借了五百萬嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我在銀行要領出來還你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五百萬？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.40,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次那個新發明的專利金已經拿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.50,0:16:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你大概是去附近的超市買東西了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就過去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.50,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了！一定是柯南跟博士聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.30,0:17:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！剛剛打電話來的那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你爺爺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五百萬…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機不可失啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦 開門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.10,0:17:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣連博士也會被抓的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了 找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那臭老頭呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從頭到尾都只有我一個人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你是強盜吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.80,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被足球打到是很痛的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是…用這雙腳力增強鞋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所踢出去的球！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？步美！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.90,0:18:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下 我現在替你鬆綁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.90,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子 幹得還真不錯嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.60,0:19:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！安全帽擋住了！這球起不了多大作用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別以為你逃得掉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小島元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圓谷光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是少年偵探團！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別小看大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成…成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.30,0:19:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團大勝利！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們立大功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.00,0:21:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯啊 步美 你感冒已經好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.60,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 聲音也恢復了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.60,0:21:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 對付步美的強盜居然不是那個強盜殺人犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.40,0:21:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人驚訝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.90,0:21:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那個強盜殺人犯已經在橫濱落網了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.70,0:22:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官說侵入步美家的兇手似乎沒有加害步美的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美還是小孩 就算他的臉被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.70,0:22:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於小孩子沒有作證的能力 對他並不構成威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他最後還是襲擊你了 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.60,0:22:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以把他抓起來才是正確的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.40,0:22:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大白癡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫做正確的做法啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.20,0:22:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次是你們運氣好 強盜才讓你們給抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.10,0:22:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後一定要等到警方抵達 才可以行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.30,0:22:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.10,0:22:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後我們一定會照辦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.30,0:22:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…知道就好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們去盪鞦韆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.00,0:22:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 走吧 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.70,0:22:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.80,0:22:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底明白了沒啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.90,0:22:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一 你也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.70,0:22:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.80,0:22:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我儘量不要把他們牽扯進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.20,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.40,0:22:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姑且不論你頭腦多聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.90,0:22:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要記住你的身體還是小學生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.50,0:22:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.70,0:23:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.70,0:23:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒打電話來 兇手就逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.70,0:23:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.40,0:23:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要用我的聲音是沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.50,0:23:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我還不至於老到當爺爺吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.90,0:23:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.00,0:23:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 如果有那麼可愛的孫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.10,0:23:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒也別有一番風趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.30,0:23:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 爺爺幫你們推秋千吧 來來～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.00,0:23:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全變成爺爺的樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.20,0:23:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其在那邊想孫子 不如先找個妻子吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.30,0:23:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！哥梅拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.90,0:23:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.60,0:23:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有個黑影在晃動耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.20,0:24:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？光彥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.40,0:24:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.10,0:24:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集的柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.40,0:24:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後的上映殺人事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.00,0:24:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官的NEXT CONAN’S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.70,0:24:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電影院的空調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.80,0:24:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次的舞臺是電影院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.40,0:24:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和佐藤警官何時才能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.10,0:24:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好難為情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.76,0:00:17.47,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR LOVE  QUEST FOR DREAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.85,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR ALL TRUTH!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.01,0:00:21.93,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有藏在眼神中的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.06,0:00:24.85,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也無法奪走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.14,0:00:31.57,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就優雅地擁抱這個真相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.74,0:00:43.37,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺肩上的溫暖 和你那不止的淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.58,0:00:49.63,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就在黎明之前 要脫胎換骨 讓自己變得更強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.92,0:00:55.76,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,縱使兩人海角天涯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.14,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,也能夠讓時間停止 找到彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.30,0:01:02.26,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有愛存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.39,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR LOVE  QUEST FOR DREAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.89,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR ALL TRUTH!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.06,0:01:09.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無法制止的熱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:12.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,吸引著我倆追求的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.03,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這份情感的由來 正是你和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.32,0:01:17.78,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR LOVE  QUEST FOR DREAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.82,0:01:19.28,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR ALL TRUTH!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有藏在眼神中的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也無法奪走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.62,0:01:31.88,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就優雅地擁抱這個真相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:20.63,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個看似有事即將發生的夜裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.17,0:20:25.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,不要閉上雙眼 誠心祝禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.09,0:20:31.64,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽曾經說過 月光如此澄澈的夜裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.26,0:20:38.02,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是因愛而出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.57,0:20:49.28,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,接著一切都停滯不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.91,0:20:55.58,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的未來已經碎為片片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.87,0:21:04.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,來 打著赤腳 輕踢大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.46,0:21:09.76,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,越過彩虹 抓住天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.55,0:21:16.27,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wish 緊緊握住胸口的十字架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.39,0:21:22.52,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在白天 用希望照耀著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.69,0:21:28.74,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在夜晚 以溫柔的光芒將你輕輕包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.90,0:21:35.53,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever still for you, still for you love
